Package: gsm.safety
Title: Safety Visualizations for Good Statistical Monitoring Workflows
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("obot", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "obot@users.noreply.github.com")
  )
Description: HTML widget bindings for the 'safety.viz' JavaScript chart
    library, providing six interactive clinical safety displays -
    histogram, shift plot, delta-delta, results over time, outlier
    explorer, and adverse event timelines - as htmlwidgets, plus bundled
    example data and report workflows for Good Statistical Monitoring.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/jwildfire/gsm.safety
